WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:25.850 --> 01:27.480
It was a ruse, silly.

01:30.980 --> 01:32.310
That was despicable.

01:33.180 --> 01:34.870
I didn't know you'd risk your life

01:34.870 --> 01:36.180
for a document.

01:36.630 --> 01:37.990
But thankfully, I saved you.

01:38.180 --> 01:39.660
So, we are even now.

01:41.050 --> 01:42.450
Just you wait. I'll prove you wrong.

01:45.430 --> 01:46.220
Sch.

02:06.660 --> 02:07.460
Sheng.

02:09.100 --> 02:10.740
I've heard all about what you did

02:10.740 --> 02:12.060
at the swimming pool.

02:12.340 --> 02:14.060
Don't bully Qiao Qingyu.

02:17.700 --> 02:19.550
She's gone through a lot.

02:24.380 --> 02:25.100
Hand it over.

02:26.140 --> 02:26.590
Hand it over.

02:39.860 --> 02:41.300
Did you tell the others?

02:42.110 --> 02:43.110
What do you mean?

02:43.110 --> 02:45.420
Did you tell the school
about Qiao Beiyu's death?

02:55.410 --> 03:00.410
[Episode 3]
[Clues from Nanqiao Village]

03:08.500 --> 03:10.340
Seeing from the result
on your laboratory sheet, you are fine.

03:11.550 --> 03:13.750
It's normal that young girls
want to be beautiful.

03:13.750 --> 03:15.140
But you can't go on a diet blindly.

03:16.990 --> 03:17.860
Let me prescribe you some medicine

03:17.860 --> 03:18.940
to nourish your spleen and stomach.

03:19.500 --> 03:20.860
But you need to exercise more.

03:21.470 --> 03:22.500
You are not fat.

03:23.670 --> 03:25.890
Doctor, I would like to ask you
about something.

03:25.940 --> 03:27.630
Did a person named Qiao Beiyu

03:27.630 --> 03:29.829
pass away at the People's Hospital
last year from an appendectomy?

03:31.180 --> 03:33.020
We can't disclose a patient's privacy.

03:33.570 --> 03:34.690
Moreover, who is she to you?

03:34.690 --> 03:35.570
She is my sister.

03:36.140 --> 03:36.790
I see.

03:37.250 --> 03:38.690
You should ask her attending physician

03:38.690 --> 03:39.650
for more information.

03:40.140 --> 03:41.740
But no one has passed away
in our hospital

03:41.950 --> 03:44.510
due to appendectomy
for more than 20 years already.

03:48.410 --> 03:53.440
[Dermatology Treatment Room 1]

04:17.390 --> 04:18.810
[Cherish Your Life and Prevent AIDS.]

04:18.810 --> 04:19.529
I'm here to...

04:19.529 --> 04:20.970
I don't care why you are here.

04:25.610 --> 04:26.930
Are you here to visit your dad?

04:27.330 --> 04:28.490
That's none of your business.

04:28.490 --> 04:30.130
Can you really retrieve
Qiao Beiyu's medical record?

04:30.130 --> 04:30.810
No.

04:31.610 --> 04:32.530
Please. I beg of you.

04:33.730 --> 04:35.370
As I said, I can't do it.

04:36.090 --> 04:37.130
You have the means
to find out the truth.

04:37.130 --> 04:38.370
So why refuse to tell me?

04:38.730 --> 04:40.370
So that you can continue
to spread rumors about me?

04:40.370 --> 04:41.290
Stop overthinking it.

04:42.170 --> 04:43.570
A patient's medical records are private.

04:44.490 --> 04:45.930
Besides, I don't have
a good relationship with my dad.

04:55.290 --> 04:56.330
Doctor, I beg of you.

04:56.330 --> 04:57.770
Please save Qian.

04:58.050 --> 04:58.970
She's only 28.

04:58.990 --> 05:00.860
We don't want to give up on her.

05:01.250 --> 05:02.690
Doctor, I beg of you.

05:02.690 --> 05:05.070
Please save her.

05:06.050 --> 05:07.250
Calm down.

05:07.990 --> 05:09.130
Given the patient's symptoms,

05:09.130 --> 05:10.900
we need to have a discussion first

05:11.010 --> 05:12.330
before we can provide an answer.

05:12.790 --> 05:13.990
Please calm down, okay?

05:14.370 --> 05:15.790
Please save her.

05:15.790 --> 05:17.670
I beg of you.

05:17.670 --> 05:18.650
Please don't do this.

05:18.890 --> 05:19.450
I implore you.

05:19.450 --> 05:20.850
We'll hold the meeting right away,

05:20.850 --> 05:21.450
okay?

05:21.460 --> 05:22.210
Please.

05:22.620 --> 05:23.460
Wait a moment.

05:24.180 --> 05:25.070
Doctor.

05:25.070 --> 05:27.130
Doctor, please save her.

05:27.390 --> 05:28.700
I beg of you.

05:28.700 --> 05:30.230
Doctor, please.

05:30.230 --> 05:32.450
Please get up first.

05:32.580 --> 05:33.290
I beg of you.

05:33.290 --> 05:34.409
If we've decided to take her in,

05:34.409 --> 05:35.490
we'll do our best to treat her.

05:35.790 --> 05:37.700
Please get up.

05:38.170 --> 05:39.420
Calm down and let's talk.

05:39.420 --> 05:40.670
Get up.

05:40.990 --> 05:41.790
Don't worry.

05:47.690 --> 05:49.170
I've transferred your monthly allowances
to your bank card.

05:52.690 --> 05:54.409
Here's the art or science stream
application form.

05:55.330 --> 05:56.130
Sign it.

06:05.210 --> 06:06.760
[Senior High Art or Science Stream
Application Form: Art ×, Science √]

06:07.670 --> 06:08.820
Why did you choose for me?

06:14.370 --> 06:15.250
Science stream suits you better.

06:16.210 --> 06:17.610
My career plan for you

06:18.130 --> 06:19.130
is to become a doctor,

06:19.930 --> 06:20.850
just like me.

06:21.030 --> 06:22.410
I want to be an art student.

06:22.530 --> 06:24.710
You got the first prize
in the national biology competition.

06:26.290 --> 06:27.050
Did you know

06:27.050 --> 06:28.990
why I took part in the competition?

06:29.550 --> 06:30.670
Did you know why I worked so hard

06:30.670 --> 06:31.910
to get first place?

06:34.330 --> 06:35.530
Because I wanted to prove to you

06:35.810 --> 06:37.170
that it's not because I can't do it.

06:37.450 --> 06:38.610
But because I hate it.

06:39.409 --> 06:40.650
I hate the medical field.

06:40.930 --> 06:42.010
I hate you.

06:42.450 --> 06:43.690
I don't need you to manage me!

06:49.570 --> 06:50.690
You put so much effort into it.

06:51.450 --> 06:52.690
You would rather sacrifice your future

06:52.690 --> 06:53.690
just to anger me.

06:55.770 --> 06:56.570
Sheng.

06:56.820 --> 06:58.230
This is not being capable.

06:58.490 --> 06:59.650
This is being childish.

07:02.450 --> 07:04.530
Parent's opinion is required, right?

07:05.130 --> 07:06.300
This is my decision.

07:06.300 --> 07:07.940
Your decision is to force your opinion

07:07.940 --> 07:09.970
on others, right?

07:10.150 --> 07:11.380
You don't care about others' feelings.

07:13.500 --> 07:14.940
When you chased my mom out

07:15.260 --> 07:16.550
and took off my grandpa's ventilator,

07:16.550 --> 07:17.620
you were like this too, right?

07:19.550 --> 07:21.300
You think your white coat
gives you the right

07:21.300 --> 07:22.930
to interfere with people's lives
however you want?

07:23.180 --> 07:24.420
You are not a doctor.

07:24.420 --> 07:25.230
You are a murderer!

07:29.890 --> 07:30.690
Shut up.

07:31.110 --> 07:32.380
The girl who passed away last year.

07:32.740 --> 07:34.740
Qiao Beiyu. You remember her, right?

07:35.260 --> 07:36.180
Do you dare say
that what happened to her

07:36.180 --> 07:37.710
had nothing to do with you?

07:41.030 --> 07:42.060
I will not get into the medical field.

07:43.110 --> 07:43.860
I won't become someone

07:43.860 --> 07:45.060
as disgusting as you.

08:07.810 --> 08:09.130
We'll be busy tonight.

08:09.490 --> 08:11.250
We've received an order
from a nearby construction site.

08:11.330 --> 08:12.530
There are more than 100 people.

08:14.890 --> 08:16.210
No need to wait for us for dinner.

08:20.290 --> 08:21.890
Cook at home.

08:23.170 --> 08:24.050
Fry an egg.

08:24.170 --> 08:25.370
There's milk in the fridge.

08:27.770 --> 08:28.770
Your health matters the most.

08:30.170 --> 08:30.970
I'll get going now.

08:35.850 --> 08:36.330
Oh, my.

08:36.530 --> 08:37.929
This dish-washing liquid
is still usable.

08:37.929 --> 08:40.169
We can use it for another week
by adding some water.

08:49.170 --> 08:49.690
Qingyu.

08:51.410 --> 08:52.300
What are you doing?

09:04.090 --> 09:04.890
By the way,

09:05.170 --> 09:06.570
wake Jinyu up.

09:06.570 --> 09:07.730
Don't forget to hang the laundry.

09:23.010 --> 09:25.170
I don't care about your gender.

09:25.170 --> 09:26.650
If I challenge you,

09:26.650 --> 09:28.450
do you dare accept my challenge,

09:28.490 --> 09:30.090
Qiao Qingyu?

09:30.090 --> 09:31.330
Are you crazy?

09:35.530 --> 09:37.130
You are no fun.

09:42.060 --> 09:43.620
I went to
the People's Hospital yesterday.

09:44.470 --> 09:45.230
Are you sick?

09:49.470 --> 09:50.860
You went to investigate Beiyu's case?

09:53.470 --> 09:55.830
I asked many doctors and nurses.

09:56.190 --> 09:57.350
All of them told me

09:57.350 --> 09:57.910
no one had passed away

09:57.910 --> 09:59.470
from an appendectomy
at People's Hospital in the past years.

09:59.930 --> 10:00.730
Well,

10:01.210 --> 10:04.250
did our parents and Jinrui lie to us?

10:05.210 --> 10:06.250
I don't know either.

10:07.730 --> 10:08.530
But today,

10:08.530 --> 10:10.650
I noticed the drawer
in our parents' room was locked.

10:10.770 --> 10:12.730
Our drawers
have never been locked before.

10:13.810 --> 10:16.490
Qiao Beiyu's medical bills have left us
tens of thousands of yuan in debt.

10:16.730 --> 10:18.250
We got into more debt when we moved.

10:18.250 --> 10:20.090
With our current situation,

10:20.130 --> 10:21.370
even a thief will pity us.

10:21.730 --> 10:23.490
It's indeed unnecessary
to lock the drawer.

10:23.810 --> 10:25.850
Unless there is something inside
that they are hiding from us.

10:27.930 --> 10:29.450
If we can open that drawer,

10:29.730 --> 10:31.530
I'm sure we can find something

10:31.610 --> 10:32.650
that is related to Beiyu's conditions

10:32.660 --> 10:34.620
like her medical records
or hospital receipts.

10:34.620 --> 10:37.070
I think you should forget about it.

10:37.500 --> 10:39.860
That lock is not to keep thieves away,

10:40.020 --> 10:41.950
but to keep us away.

10:43.310 --> 10:46.110
If you create more trouble now,

10:46.110 --> 10:49.260
aren't you afraid
that you'll get punished by our mom?

10:50.010 --> 10:50.970
Moreover,

10:51.850 --> 10:54.650
even if they are keeping it a secret
from us on purpose,

10:54.950 --> 10:57.470
I'm sure they have their reasons.

10:58.770 --> 10:59.650
If...

11:01.050 --> 11:04.090
Qiao Beiyu really passed away
from that kind of disease,

11:05.660 --> 11:06.690
I think it's better

11:06.830 --> 11:08.950
not to know the truth.

11:09.660 --> 11:10.500
Aren't you going

11:10.500 --> 11:11.660
to find out the truth,

11:11.660 --> 11:12.900
just because it might be painful?

11:12.900 --> 11:14.310
Then you are just lying to yourself.

11:16.070 --> 11:18.020
I can't beat you in an argument.
You're a top student, after all.

11:18.430 --> 11:21.500
I just think that we should let it go.

11:21.660 --> 11:22.830
She's already gone.

11:28.210 --> 11:31.450
Living in lies forever is pathetic.

11:32.170 --> 11:33.570
The harshest truth

11:35.170 --> 11:37.170
is better than the sweetest lie.

11:41.650 --> 11:43.530
This is the last exam
before our long holiday

11:43.530 --> 11:44.770
on the 1st of October.

11:45.050 --> 11:46.170
Make sure

11:46.170 --> 11:47.650
to do your best.

11:47.650 --> 11:51.010
Check your answer sheet
and your draft paper.

11:51.610 --> 11:52.530
I want to make this perfectly clear.

11:52.650 --> 11:54.130
Take this monthly test seriously.

11:54.530 --> 11:55.970
Treat every mock exam

11:56.010 --> 11:57.810
as the final NCEE.

11:57.810 --> 11:59.290
You have to continue to improve

11:59.290 --> 12:00.450
and train yourself, okay?

12:00.530 --> 12:01.890
Here, pass the paper down.

12:06.210 --> 12:08.130
Pay closer attention.

12:09.370 --> 12:10.330
Read the questions properly.

12:10.330 --> 12:11.450
Only start answering after you do that.

12:32.090 --> 12:34.890
When we were young,
the phrase that we always used

12:34.890 --> 12:35.890
was to grow up faster.

12:36.890 --> 12:39.650
[No Turning Back at 17]
We thought we would get better with age.

12:40.890 --> 12:43.370
But why is it that the older we get,

12:43.650 --> 12:46.770
the more confused
and troubled we become?

12:47.070 --> 12:48.490
♪You said something
I couldn't understand♪

12:48.490 --> 12:49.590
At 17,

12:50.490 --> 12:52.130
I don't want to be treated
as a young boy anymore.

12:52.490 --> 12:54.970
Even if it's
a difficult and painful path,

12:54.970 --> 12:57.130
I want to build my own strength.

12:57.720 --> 13:01.310
♪You lit up a lamp♪

13:04.290 --> 13:06.790
♪I saw the light♪

13:06.790 --> 13:08.440
[Wild and Free at 17]

13:10.120 --> 13:11.530
♪You slowly walked away♪

13:11.530 --> 13:12.330
I think

13:12.730 --> 13:15.090
that as long I pursue the absolute truth

13:15.090 --> 13:16.170
and have a clear conscience,

13:16.730 --> 13:19.530
there's no obstacle that can stop me.

13:19.530 --> 13:21.370
Although

13:21.370 --> 13:23.490
the path I'm walking on at 17
remains rough and bumpy,

13:23.930 --> 13:25.050
I know

13:25.810 --> 13:28.370
that hope and sunshine
are just right ahead.

13:43.330 --> 13:44.690
Dad, be careful.

13:47.130 --> 13:48.250
It's all wet.

13:48.250 --> 13:49.050
Yes.

13:49.730 --> 13:50.610
Look.

13:52.490 --> 13:54.250
Dad, Mom.

13:55.050 --> 13:56.570
- You are back.
- Yeah.

13:56.770 --> 13:57.850
Dad, Mom.

13:58.010 --> 13:59.090
We are back.

13:59.770 --> 14:00.970
Be careful.

14:01.250 --> 14:02.010
Greet your elders.

14:02.250 --> 14:04.330
Greetings, Grandpa, Grandma,
Uncle Haisheng.

14:04.330 --> 14:05.130
You are back.

14:06.090 --> 14:08.050
The rainstorm this year
is really terrible.

14:08.050 --> 14:10.010
Yes. We need to thank Jinrui

14:10.010 --> 14:11.650
for checking
the weather forecast every day.

14:11.810 --> 14:13.050
He warned us in advance

14:13.050 --> 14:15.610
and asked us to stay at Haisheng's.

14:15.890 --> 14:18.650
Otherwise, we wouldn't know
what could have happened to us.

14:18.810 --> 14:19.770
Okay, Mom. Put this down.

14:19.770 --> 14:20.210
Look.

14:20.210 --> 14:21.610
We'll clean these up later.

14:21.890 --> 14:22.690
Put it down.

14:23.890 --> 14:25.170
Mom, just leave these to us.

14:26.690 --> 14:28.010
Here. Look.

14:28.610 --> 14:29.810
It's okay. Place it there.

14:29.810 --> 14:30.410
You don't have to do anything.

14:30.410 --> 14:31.490
Just take a rest.

14:32.290 --> 14:33.290
Qing.

14:33.930 --> 14:36.010
You've gotten taller and slimmer.

14:36.490 --> 14:38.850
Other young girls look bright and young.

14:38.850 --> 14:41.530
Why does Qing look so pale?

14:42.290 --> 14:43.090
Fanghao.

14:43.330 --> 14:44.490
Don't just

14:44.490 --> 14:46.780
think about making money
and doing business.

14:47.090 --> 14:48.210
You need to pay more attention

14:48.410 --> 14:50.330
to your children.

14:50.330 --> 14:51.660
Mom, she takes care of them quite well.

14:52.210 --> 14:53.350
Since you are back,

14:53.530 --> 14:54.780
I'll bring them home.

14:54.850 --> 14:55.780
Okay.

14:55.970 --> 14:58.090
Dad, Mom, go and rest now.

14:58.090 --> 14:59.620
We'll clean up the old house for you.

14:59.650 --> 15:00.450
See your grandma off.

15:00.530 --> 15:01.430
Okay.

15:01.890 --> 15:02.380
Bye.

15:02.570 --> 15:03.570
Be careful. The ground is slippery.

15:03.570 --> 15:04.430
Yes.

15:05.650 --> 15:06.450
Haisheng.

15:06.570 --> 15:07.090
Hmm?

15:07.410 --> 15:08.570
We've brought something for our parents.

15:08.570 --> 15:09.690
Go back.

15:09.970 --> 15:10.780
Lusheng.

15:11.090 --> 15:13.890
I'm sorry that you have to
stay at the old house

15:13.890 --> 15:14.530
for the next few days.

15:14.530 --> 15:14.970
Take it.

15:15.290 --> 15:16.330
You shouldn't do this, Grandma.

15:16.650 --> 15:17.890
Don't let your sister find out.

15:19.730 --> 15:20.210
Okay.

15:20.210 --> 15:21.110
Keep it.

15:22.010 --> 15:22.610
Thank you, Mom.

15:22.610 --> 15:23.410
Mom, let me see you off.

15:23.530 --> 15:24.070
Okay.

15:58.450 --> 16:00.210
Don't tell me

16:00.210 --> 16:02.660
that you want to do your investigation
at the old house.

16:10.620 --> 16:12.950
This place is flooded every year
during the rainy season.

16:13.210 --> 16:15.310
This old house is run-down.

16:15.450 --> 16:16.210
Look over there.

16:16.970 --> 16:18.250
That wood is rotten.

16:20.490 --> 16:21.530
I'm thinking

16:22.650 --> 16:23.850
that after cleaning this place up,

16:23.850 --> 16:26.250
let's renovate this old house.

16:26.370 --> 16:27.330
What do you think?

16:27.530 --> 16:29.730
That way, my parents
can live more comfortably.

16:29.890 --> 16:31.450
Yes. You can renovate it
if you have the money.

16:34.130 --> 16:36.370
No. As for the money,

16:37.290 --> 16:38.730
we are young,
and we just need to work harder

16:39.370 --> 16:40.810
and save some money for the renovation.

16:40.810 --> 16:41.850
Well.

16:42.450 --> 16:44.570
You can try saving up
as much as you can.

16:47.210 --> 16:47.570
No.

16:47.690 --> 16:49.450
I'm discussing it with you.

16:50.450 --> 16:51.450
I didn't say anything.

16:51.450 --> 16:52.810
I said you could do it.

16:54.690 --> 16:56.130
Your family is the most important.

17:00.250 --> 17:01.730
We finally got a holiday.

17:02.250 --> 17:03.970
The children should have stayed home

17:04.490 --> 17:06.089
to study or rest.

17:06.650 --> 17:08.010
But you insisted that we come back.

17:08.329 --> 17:09.250
What can we do here?

17:09.250 --> 17:09.609
Enough.

17:09.609 --> 17:10.369
You always bring me trouble.

17:10.450 --> 17:10.970
Enough.

17:10.970 --> 17:12.010
Let's just get to work.

17:40.330 --> 17:40.890
Hey.

17:41.970 --> 17:42.530
Hey.

17:44.570 --> 17:45.930
Hurry up. Look.

17:45.930 --> 17:47.170
Don't interrupt me. Who is it?

17:47.930 --> 17:48.730
This is

17:49.290 --> 17:50.810
the most beautiful girl in Shunyun,

17:51.410 --> 17:52.250
Qiao Beiyu.

17:53.130 --> 17:55.050
The beautiful girl who passed away
from an illness, right?

17:55.530 --> 17:56.490
If you didn't tell me, I wouldn't know

17:56.490 --> 17:58.570
that Qiao Qingyu who just transferred
to our class was her sister.

17:58.570 --> 17:59.650
I just found out too.

17:59.890 --> 18:01.370
Are we going to play or not?

18:01.850 --> 18:02.650
- Yes.
-Yes.

18:02.730 --> 18:04.730
We can gossip for a while.
We can multitask.

18:06.050 --> 18:06.650
I heard about another thing.

18:07.410 --> 18:08.210
Qiao Beiyu

18:08.530 --> 18:09.890
looked aloof.

18:10.290 --> 18:11.130
But

18:11.370 --> 18:13.370
as long as a boy treated her kindly,

18:13.410 --> 18:15.930
he'd get to see how passionate she'd be.

18:16.930 --> 18:18.250
How do you know her so well?

18:18.410 --> 18:19.530
Are you planning to do something to her?

18:19.530 --> 18:21.050
No. I heard about it from Hei.

18:21.290 --> 18:22.410
You know who Hei is, right?

18:22.690 --> 18:23.730
He's my sworn brother.

18:24.410 --> 18:26.050
He told me that he used to
date Qiao Beiyu.

18:26.050 --> 18:27.650
Hei is your sworn brother?

18:27.770 --> 18:28.730
Why haven't I heard about it before?

18:28.970 --> 18:29.810
Is that the point here?

18:29.810 --> 18:31.090
The point here is Qiao Beiyu.

18:31.930 --> 18:32.770
Tell me.

18:32.850 --> 18:35.650
If the older sister is
the most beautiful girl in Shunyun,

18:35.650 --> 18:37.370
is the younger sister the runner-up?

18:38.050 --> 18:40.090
They both look similar.

18:40.170 --> 18:42.130
Is it possible that they share
the same personality?

18:42.690 --> 18:44.650
Is Qiao Qingyu...

18:47.410 --> 18:48.290
Why did you shoot your ball here?

18:49.570 --> 18:50.450
It was an accident.

18:51.770 --> 18:52.930
I still have things to do.
I need to leave now.

18:53.290 --> 18:54.050
You can enjoy the game yourself.

18:56.450 --> 18:57.530
What happened?

19:03.010 --> 19:05.730
I didn't tell anyone about your sister.

19:14.250 --> 19:16.810
Do you want to know
who spread the news?

19:24.050 --> 19:29.850
How is it going
with your holiday homework?

19:33.290 --> 19:33.930
Sheng.

19:35.290 --> 19:36.050
Why are you suddenly leaving?

19:36.810 --> 19:37.810
Who are you talking to right now?

19:38.410 --> 19:39.410
What has it got to do with you?

19:40.010 --> 19:40.810
It's just a mindless question.

19:44.690 --> 19:46.450
Protecting our environment,
starts with me.

19:46.690 --> 19:48.410
Find a home for trash around you.

19:49.290 --> 19:51.170
Do you want me
to find a home for you too?

19:51.610 --> 19:52.410
No.

19:53.370 --> 19:55.130
You must have sent a message to a girl.

19:56.410 --> 19:58.610
Why are you such a busybody?

19:59.570 --> 20:00.490
You should focus on yourself.

20:06.010 --> 20:07.050
Let's go and eat.

20:07.450 --> 20:08.450
Focus on yourself.

20:10.690 --> 20:11.810
Let's go.

20:24.390 --> 20:25.340
Thank you, madam.

20:25.470 --> 20:26.260
By the way,

20:26.260 --> 20:27.870
remember to add more chilies
for my sister's.

20:27.990 --> 20:28.710
Okay.

20:31.710 --> 20:32.670
Ms. Xuehua.

20:33.580 --> 20:35.210
There's something I would like to ask.

20:36.130 --> 20:37.210
What is it? Tell me.

20:37.650 --> 20:39.090
It's about Qiao Beiyu.

20:46.650 --> 20:48.650
Everyone says
that she was a femme fatale.

20:48.650 --> 20:51.250
But I think she was just a pretty girl
with an unfortunate life.

20:52.650 --> 20:54.210
She was sent to the countryside

20:54.490 --> 20:56.210
at such a young age.

20:57.150 --> 20:58.340
Your parents were terrible too.

20:59.190 --> 21:00.950
They didn't come back to visit her
for months at a time.

21:02.300 --> 21:03.540
And your grandparents

21:04.190 --> 21:05.580
were old already.

21:05.580 --> 21:07.540
They didn't have the energy
or the capability to take care of her.

21:10.020 --> 21:10.990
In this village,

21:11.230 --> 21:12.950
she was like a wild child.

21:19.820 --> 21:21.910
But it was strange.

21:22.490 --> 21:25.130
A wild child who no one cared about

21:25.370 --> 21:27.610
grew up to be prettier and prettier.

21:27.780 --> 21:29.150
And she danced so well.

21:29.990 --> 21:31.500
She was so talented.

21:31.820 --> 21:33.230
I heard

21:33.340 --> 21:37.060
that she was scouted
by the dance academy in Beining.

21:37.470 --> 21:38.540
I don't know

21:38.540 --> 21:40.740
why she would end up
at Huanzhou Art School.

21:40.950 --> 21:43.540
I heard that it was a junior college.
What a pity.

21:59.990 --> 22:01.540
Look, Qingyu.

22:36.240 --> 22:37.870
[For Qingyu]

22:37.870 --> 22:38.670
Well,

22:38.670 --> 22:41.020
you rarely came back to Nanqiao Village
when you were young.

22:42.190 --> 22:43.990
Your sister was always waiting for you.

22:44.540 --> 22:46.260
She would keep
all the good things for you.

22:50.430 --> 22:51.950
Qingyu, Jinyu, come out for a while.

23:00.300 --> 23:01.390
Throw away that feather lamp

23:01.390 --> 23:03.230
and other useless things.

23:03.710 --> 23:05.500
You want us to throw away
that floor lamp?

23:06.100 --> 23:07.470
It is in good condition.

23:07.470 --> 23:08.990
We just need to change the bulb.

23:09.390 --> 23:10.340
Just throw it away if I say so.

23:11.430 --> 23:13.670
This was Beiyu's favorite lamp
when she was still alive.

23:13.990 --> 23:15.060
And I remember

23:15.060 --> 23:17.100
that it was a gift from Jinrui.

23:17.340 --> 23:18.670
Did you not hear me?

23:19.670 --> 23:20.910
These are just useless things.

23:21.020 --> 23:21.990
Beautiful but useless.

23:23.580 --> 23:24.580
It must have weathered the flood

23:24.580 --> 23:25.740
more than once at least.

23:25.910 --> 23:26.910
We should've thrown it out
a long time ago.

23:48.100 --> 23:50.820
Actually, it's nice staying
in this old house.

23:51.390 --> 23:53.260
If I didn't lose my job
at the power supply station

23:53.260 --> 23:54.710
back then,

23:55.020 --> 23:56.500
it would be nice for our family
to live here together.

23:57.540 --> 23:58.540
We wouldn't have to be so exhausted.

24:00.470 --> 24:01.630
We wouldn't have to take care
of the noodle shop

24:01.630 --> 24:02.950
while raising our kids.

24:04.580 --> 24:06.430
And Bei would not be separated from us.

24:13.190 --> 24:14.820
I remember that when we were young,

24:16.020 --> 24:17.740
whenever we returned to Nanqiao Village,

24:18.150 --> 24:20.540
she would keep
all the good food and fun toys

24:20.540 --> 24:21.630
for us.

24:23.910 --> 24:24.500
If

24:25.300 --> 24:27.780
Qiao Beiyu had stayed with us

24:28.100 --> 24:29.990
and our parents in Shunyun back then,

24:30.740 --> 24:31.540
how would she have turned out?

24:32.630 --> 24:33.820
Our grandparents always told us

24:35.150 --> 24:36.820
that our parents

24:37.150 --> 24:38.500
couldn't raise the three of us together.

24:38.950 --> 24:39.540
So,

24:40.470 --> 24:42.390
Beiyu was left behind
at Nanqiao Village.

24:43.740 --> 24:46.540
If it was me or you who was left behind
at Nanqiao Village,

24:46.950 --> 24:48.870
would Qiao Beiyu have an easier life?

24:52.940 --> 24:55.490
[Certificate: Qiao Beiyu]

25:00.500 --> 25:01.020
Fanghao.

25:02.020 --> 25:02.430
Fanghao.

25:02.910 --> 25:03.710
Look.

25:07.260 --> 25:09.430
[First Prize in Essay Writing]
One time, you told Bei

25:09.740 --> 25:11.150
that if she got a prize
in essay writing,

25:11.150 --> 25:12.740
we would take her to Mount Wumu.

25:13.430 --> 25:15.500
In the end, we didn't go
because we were too busy

25:15.500 --> 25:16.260
on National Day.

25:16.540 --> 25:17.540
I called her and told her

25:17.540 --> 25:18.340
that we couldn't make it.

25:18.340 --> 25:18.820
She told me

25:19.670 --> 25:20.100
that it was okay

25:20.910 --> 25:21.950
because she didn't win a prize.

25:35.950 --> 25:37.670
She actually won a prize.

25:37.870 --> 25:40.260
But she didn't tell us about it.

25:41.190 --> 25:43.580
What were we thinking?

25:45.060 --> 25:47.260
Why didn't we try harder for her?

25:49.390 --> 25:51.230
We already had Yu at that time.

25:51.950 --> 25:53.340
If we had insisted,

25:53.340 --> 25:54.710
maybe my dad would've agreed

25:54.710 --> 25:56.300
to let us take Bei back with us.

25:58.430 --> 26:00.100
And the rest wouldn't have happened.

26:04.060 --> 26:06.100
I don't know when it all started.

26:06.630 --> 26:07.820
But Qiao Beiyu turned

26:07.820 --> 26:09.500
into a total sinner.

26:09.580 --> 26:12.580
Mom would go berserk
when she talked about her.

26:12.870 --> 26:15.340
And dad would shake his head and sigh
when talking about her.

26:16.390 --> 26:17.500
I hated her too.

26:18.190 --> 26:20.150
I hated how she stood out in everything,

26:20.540 --> 26:22.470
making me look like a meek

26:22.470 --> 26:23.710
and indecisive person.

26:24.060 --> 26:25.150
But it was true

26:25.820 --> 26:27.340
that she would protect you
when you were hit.

26:28.190 --> 26:30.300
And she kept all the sweets for me.

26:31.890 --> 26:32.710
Enough.

26:32.910 --> 26:34.820
Stop being sentimental.

26:34.820 --> 26:36.150
The dead cannot be resurrected.

26:36.150 --> 26:37.500
Beiyu is gone now.

26:37.780 --> 26:39.340
Let bygones be bygones.

26:52.780 --> 26:53.500
Mr. Sun,

26:53.500 --> 26:54.390
I would send

26:54.390 --> 26:55.950
the application form to you
this afternoon.

26:55.950 --> 26:57.540
My dad was on a business trip.

26:57.540 --> 26:58.540
So, I couldn't get him to sign.

26:59.190 --> 26:59.950
Don't worry.

26:59.950 --> 27:02.230
I'll give it to you
before your holiday training is over.

27:03.950 --> 27:04.390
Okay.

27:08.180 --> 27:08.850
Let me see.

27:09.010 --> 27:10.900
Here. Look at mine.

27:12.010 --> 27:12.940
Why is there an English name?

27:13.490 --> 27:15.050
Your dad is the president
of the hospital, right?

27:15.290 --> 27:17.050
So, his signature
should have a more Western flair.

27:17.490 --> 27:18.220
You are nuts.

27:26.810 --> 27:27.490
Sign here.

27:31.310 --> 27:33.390
[Parent/Guardian Signature]

27:37.750 --> 27:38.380
How is it?

27:39.020 --> 27:39.820
Yes.

27:40.650 --> 27:41.450
What do you think?

27:41.730 --> 27:43.320
I think it's just okay.

27:43.520 --> 27:44.650
It's way better than yours.

27:44.650 --> 27:45.970
Look at what you signed.

27:46.080 --> 27:47.450
At least he signed in Chinese.

27:48.360 --> 27:49.360
It's easy to fool Sun.

27:49.840 --> 27:51.800
You should think
about how to handle your dad.

27:51.970 --> 27:53.360
It's okay. My dad doesn't care about me.

27:53.360 --> 27:54.320
And he can't control me.

27:54.320 --> 27:54.930
Fine.

27:54.930 --> 27:55.840
Everyone has handed in
their application form

27:55.840 --> 27:57.180
except you.

27:57.180 --> 27:57.770
Hand it in

27:57.770 --> 27:58.780
before the holiday is over.

27:58.780 --> 27:59.530
Okay.

28:15.150 --> 28:16.460
You put so much effort into it.

28:17.150 --> 28:18.590
You would rather sacrifice your future

28:18.590 --> 28:19.820
just to anger me.

28:20.540 --> 28:21.910
This is not being capable.

28:22.220 --> 28:23.390
This is being childish.

28:23.390 --> 28:26.330
[Senior High Art or Science Stream
Application Form]

28:43.950 --> 28:44.500
Hey, buddy.

28:44.870 --> 28:45.350
Lusheng.

28:45.710 --> 28:46.190
You are back.

28:47.350 --> 28:47.870
Fanghao.

28:49.150 --> 28:50.350
Haisheng told me that you came back.

28:50.820 --> 28:51.670
When did you arrive?

28:51.740 --> 28:52.190
This morning.

28:52.710 --> 28:54.630
We came here
by taking the first bus here.

28:54.910 --> 28:55.780
You came back right on time.

28:56.150 --> 28:56.980
Let's eat.

28:56.980 --> 28:58.390
There's soup too. I'll serve it now.

28:58.390 --> 28:59.430
We can start eating soon.

29:00.110 --> 29:01.020
You came all the way here,

29:01.780 --> 29:03.260
and you even cooked for us.

29:03.430 --> 29:04.190
Don't worry about it.

29:04.190 --> 29:04.980
Have a seat.

29:05.150 --> 29:05.540
Have a seat.

29:06.670 --> 29:08.060
Uncle, Aunt.

29:08.740 --> 29:09.630
Here's the soup.

29:10.780 --> 29:11.430
Bei?

29:15.350 --> 29:15.780
Bei!

29:16.710 --> 29:17.530
No. She is not Bei.

29:17.530 --> 29:17.730
Wenqiu.

29:17.950 --> 29:18.220
Bei!

29:18.540 --> 29:18.820
Wenqiu.

29:18.820 --> 29:19.150
Well...

29:19.300 --> 29:19.740
Aunt.

29:20.460 --> 29:20.670
Dad.

29:21.190 --> 29:21.430
Let her go.

29:21.590 --> 29:23.110
She is Qingyu, not Beiyu.

29:23.300 --> 29:23.670
You are back.

29:23.670 --> 29:23.980
Aunt.

29:24.300 --> 29:25.190
- Wenqiu.
- Let her go.

29:25.350 --> 29:26.190
I've missed you so much, Bei.

29:26.190 --> 29:26.910
Let her go.

29:26.950 --> 29:27.430
Bei.

29:27.430 --> 29:27.910
Aunt.

29:28.110 --> 29:28.950
Are the flowers beautiful?

29:28.950 --> 29:29.540
Let her go first.

29:29.540 --> 29:30.350
Are the flowers pretty?

29:30.350 --> 29:31.060
Aunt.

29:31.060 --> 29:31.820
You are crushing the flowers.

29:32.060 --> 29:33.950
Flowers.

29:34.280 --> 29:35.950
Flowers.

29:36.820 --> 29:37.350
Bei.

29:38.780 --> 29:39.220
Bei.

29:40.390 --> 29:40.980
Let's eat.

29:41.980 --> 29:42.540
Let's eat.

29:43.350 --> 29:43.980
You go ahead.

29:44.500 --> 29:45.390
I'll eat with her in our room.

29:46.220 --> 29:47.950
Come, let's eat first.

29:49.500 --> 29:50.260
Let's eat first.

29:55.590 --> 29:56.260
Are you okay?

29:58.870 --> 29:59.350
Let's go.

30:00.820 --> 30:01.260
Bei.

30:02.020 --> 30:03.820
After dinner,
we can get her some flowers.

30:22.980 --> 30:23.540
Well...

30:24.220 --> 30:25.910
Fanghao, Lusheng.

30:26.300 --> 30:27.870
Wenqiu was out of sorts.

30:28.460 --> 30:29.710
She didn't frighten Qingyu, right?

30:29.710 --> 30:31.220
It's fine.

30:31.460 --> 30:32.500
Just drink.

30:41.980 --> 30:44.590
It seems like Qin is still

30:44.950 --> 30:45.430
a little bit...

30:48.020 --> 30:49.630
Ever since our child is gone,

30:51.500 --> 30:52.350
she fell sick.

30:53.190 --> 30:53.950
Mentally.

30:55.350 --> 30:56.630
We went to many doctors.

30:57.440 --> 30:58.760
They told me it was a mental illness

31:00.240 --> 31:00.830
and couldn't be treated.

31:02.760 --> 31:04.110
It must be difficult for you.

31:06.040 --> 31:07.670
Gosh, slow down.

31:09.350 --> 31:10.390
I'm happy that you are back.

31:13.780 --> 31:15.220
At first, I wanted to get married,

31:16.630 --> 31:17.390
have children,

31:17.390 --> 31:18.740
and live a quiet life.

31:21.390 --> 31:23.150
Wenqiu loves children too.

31:24.150 --> 31:25.220
But with her like this now,

31:25.980 --> 31:27.430
we can't have a child.

31:28.500 --> 31:29.540
She can't be without me.

31:30.590 --> 31:31.460
I've accepted that.

31:32.710 --> 31:33.870
I can't be without her either.

31:34.670 --> 31:35.390
Buddy.

31:36.190 --> 31:37.950
Each family has its own difficulty.

31:38.500 --> 31:39.220
It's life.

31:39.460 --> 31:40.740
Things will get better through time.

31:45.980 --> 31:46.950
You have it good.

31:48.110 --> 31:49.630
You have Qing and Yu.

31:50.190 --> 31:51.820
They will grow up in a few more years.

31:52.390 --> 31:54.020
But now that I think about it,

31:54.110 --> 31:55.780
Qing has grown up quite quickly.

31:56.740 --> 31:58.500
I couldn't recognize her
when I came in just now.

31:59.500 --> 32:00.870
I thought she was Beiyu too.

32:05.190 --> 32:06.300
That's not true.

32:10.670 --> 32:11.820
Enjoy your drinks.

32:17.460 --> 32:18.110
Lusheng.

32:19.540 --> 32:20.540
I didn't mean anything by that.

32:22.020 --> 32:24.710
It's tough keeping tabs on girls
once they're grown.

32:24.950 --> 32:26.220
You need to keep an eye on her.

32:30.020 --> 32:30.710
Buddy, you...

32:32.020 --> 32:32.680
Drink.

32:38.430 --> 32:38.910
I...

32:39.500 --> 32:40.060
Let's just drink.

32:47.540 --> 32:49.190
Before Beiyu attended
the art school in Huanzhou,

32:49.590 --> 32:50.820
she had been staying here.

32:51.590 --> 32:53.590
She was very close with Aunt Qin.

32:54.350 --> 32:55.670
They lived together for so many years.

32:55.980 --> 32:57.060
I'm sure they were close.

32:57.980 --> 33:00.590
No wonder she would mistake you
for Beiyu today.

33:01.460 --> 33:03.300
When Aunt Qin hugged me today,

33:03.710 --> 33:04.910
she hugged me very tightly.

33:05.390 --> 33:07.190
And she failed to say a word.

33:08.870 --> 33:10.390
She's mentally ill.

33:10.980 --> 33:11.980
Don't let it bother you.

33:12.500 --> 33:14.020
But I think she was sincere.

33:14.710 --> 33:16.670
I think she really treated Beiyu well.

33:17.260 --> 33:18.540
Unfortunately, Qiao Beiyu...

33:20.190 --> 33:22.150
It's really a pity.

33:23.780 --> 33:25.590
People only ever say bad things

33:25.710 --> 33:26.910
about Qiao Beiyu.

33:27.670 --> 33:29.820
Only Aunt Qin was on her side.

33:31.190 --> 33:31.710
What do you think

33:32.980 --> 33:34.590
happened to Qiao Beiyu

33:34.590 --> 33:35.870
back then

33:35.980 --> 33:37.780
to make Aunt Qin pity her so much?

33:50.390 --> 33:50.670
Sheng.

33:51.950 --> 33:52.220
Sheng.

33:57.460 --> 33:57.980
Sheng!

33:58.630 --> 33:59.060
Sheng.

33:59.870 --> 34:00.910
I live upstream,

34:01.430 --> 34:02.500
while you live downstream.

34:03.060 --> 34:03.980
I'm in science,

34:04.460 --> 34:05.220
while you're in arts.

34:05.710 --> 34:07.220
The two of us are like parallel lines

34:07.220 --> 34:08.500
who will never cross paths again.

34:08.820 --> 34:09.500
I suffer

34:09.500 --> 34:10.670
when I think about that.

34:10.820 --> 34:11.820
I can't help myself.

34:12.429 --> 34:13.500
You are so dramatic.

34:14.060 --> 34:14.739
Sheng.

34:15.060 --> 34:16.300
Even if you're in arts,

34:16.300 --> 34:17.389
we're still friends.

34:18.429 --> 34:19.500
Let's eat together tonight.

34:19.500 --> 34:20.350
A farewell dinner for you.

34:22.219 --> 34:23.020
After thinking it over,

34:23.429 --> 34:24.870
I'll go with science.

34:25.110 --> 34:25.909
What?

34:26.060 --> 34:26.870
Have you finally thought it through?

34:27.710 --> 34:28.540
Why do I feel

34:28.540 --> 34:29.780
like you don't welcome me?

34:30.500 --> 34:31.590
Are you afraid
that I'll steal your limelight?

34:31.710 --> 34:32.630
No.

34:32.870 --> 34:34.150
We just don't understand.

34:34.540 --> 34:36.110
I thought you wanted
to fight against your dad.

34:36.460 --> 34:37.780
When have you become
so obedient out of the blue?

34:38.350 --> 34:39.630
I made that decision for myself.

34:40.150 --> 34:40.780
It has nothing to do with him.

34:46.710 --> 34:48.110
You should warm up first, bro.

35:12.030 --> 35:16.150
[Nanqiao Village Community Center]

35:16.230 --> 35:17.280
[Literature]

35:36.680 --> 35:38.280
[Qiao Beiyu]

35:38.780 --> 35:44.910
[Love is the brightest element here.
But it's also the start of a disaster.]

35:51.990 --> 35:52.820
Qingyu.

35:55.860 --> 35:56.740
Ma Mingkai.

36:01.420 --> 36:04.110
I came to see my grandparents

36:04.110 --> 36:05.340
for the holiday.

36:07.550 --> 36:08.110
Well,

36:09.030 --> 36:10.550
we haven't met in a long time, right?

36:14.670 --> 36:15.190
By the way,

36:16.550 --> 36:17.630
why didn't you reply

36:19.110 --> 36:20.510
to the letters I sent you?

36:21.260 --> 36:22.940
I didn't receive any letters.

36:25.300 --> 36:26.550
Maybe they were delivered
to the wrong address.

36:26.900 --> 36:28.510
After all, who writes letters
these days?

36:30.420 --> 36:31.030
Anyway,

36:31.740 --> 36:33.300
everything is good
as long as you are not doing it

36:33.300 --> 36:33.990
on purpose.

36:35.070 --> 36:36.340
Why did you write?

36:38.300 --> 36:39.670
Nothing special.

36:43.710 --> 36:44.630
Qingyu.

36:44.940 --> 36:46.070
Let's study at the library

36:46.780 --> 36:48.510
tomorrow morning.

36:49.070 --> 36:49.820
Since you're doing great academically,

36:50.740 --> 36:52.420
I can ask you when I have questions
that I don't understand.

36:55.030 --> 36:55.710
Ma Mingkai.

36:56.110 --> 36:56.670
Thank you.

36:58.220 --> 36:58.820
Why are you thanking me?

36:59.470 --> 37:00.900
Thank you for willing
to hang out with me.

37:01.820 --> 37:02.740
Actually, I've heard

37:03.190 --> 37:04.070
about that too.

37:04.860 --> 37:05.940
But Beiyu is Beiyu.

37:05.940 --> 37:06.630
You are you.

37:06.900 --> 37:07.990
I can't blame you

37:07.990 --> 37:08.780
for what Beiyu did.

37:09.260 --> 37:09.900
Moreover,

37:11.380 --> 37:12.420
the Qingyu I know

37:13.030 --> 37:14.710
is a top student
with good personality and grades.

37:15.260 --> 37:16.590
You'd never do something improper.

37:17.110 --> 37:18.740
You are obedient and well-behaved.

37:19.820 --> 37:21.740
What do you mean by that?

37:22.070 --> 37:22.860
I mean

37:23.260 --> 37:24.780
you are different from your sister.

37:28.070 --> 37:29.340
I have things to do today.

37:29.340 --> 37:30.150
I need to get going.

37:33.740 --> 37:34.740
I'll see you tomorrow, then.

38:02.590 --> 38:03.470
[Authorization for Medical Records]
If...

38:04.150 --> 38:07.420
Qiao Beiyu really passed away
from that kind of disease,

38:07.630 --> 38:10.630
I think it's better
not to know the truth.

38:12.580 --> 38:13.060
Good shot.

38:13.700 --> 38:14.580
Enough.

38:14.580 --> 38:15.350
We can't defeat you.

38:15.350 --> 38:16.270
We'll stop now. Let's go.

38:16.750 --> 38:18.020
Let's go home.

38:18.020 --> 38:19.100
- See you next time.
- Bye.

38:19.100 --> 38:19.910
See you.

38:32.310 --> 38:33.100
A washboard shot.

38:33.840 --> 38:36.260
[Qiao Qingyu: Did you steal the letters
that Ma Mingkai sent to me?]

38:36.260 --> 38:37.600
[I asked our class monitor.]

38:37.600 --> 38:39.110
[You were in charge
of delivering the letters]

38:39.110 --> 38:40.910
[to our class last month.]

38:42.340 --> 38:45.550
[Ming Sheng:
I didn't steal your letters.]

38:45.550 --> 38:48.610
[Don't accuse an innocent man!]

38:50.760 --> 38:54.360
[Authorization for Medical Records]

39:00.460 --> 39:02.460
[Qiao Qingyu: Then give me a hand.]

39:02.460 --> 39:04.440
[I want my sister's medical records.]

39:04.440 --> 39:06.960
[I've written the authorization letter
to release her medical records to me.]

39:12.560 --> 39:15.910
[Ming Sheng: I can only apply
to get a copy of her medical records.]

39:15.910 --> 39:17.640
[If I managed to get it for you,]

39:17.640 --> 39:19.060
[how are you going to thank me?]

39:20.010 --> 39:22.760
[Qiao Qingyu:
How do you want me to thank you?]

39:23.830 --> 39:25.020
Sheng.

39:29.390 --> 39:30.750
Look at his raised brows

39:32.100 --> 39:33.540
and his smiling lips.

39:34.620 --> 39:35.830
Those are the symptoms.

39:39.140 --> 39:40.140
He's been possessed.

39:46.050 --> 39:49.200
[Authorization to Release
Medical Records of Qiao Beiyu]

40:04.910 --> 40:05.950
Ms. Xiuzhen.

40:06.580 --> 40:08.740
Qing, you are so tall now.

40:08.740 --> 40:09.260
My uncle

40:09.260 --> 40:10.470
and parents are out.

40:10.470 --> 40:11.510
They aren't home yet.

40:11.580 --> 40:12.660
It's okay.

40:12.780 --> 40:14.990
Your uncle asked me
to check on Qin.

40:45.250 --> 40:46.040
How is she?

40:46.410 --> 40:47.410
She's fine.

40:48.520 --> 40:51.250
I am just a clinic health worker.

40:51.250 --> 40:53.040
I don't know how to treat this illness.

40:53.040 --> 40:54.680
Your uncle wants me to check on her

40:54.680 --> 40:55.850
so that he can feel more at ease.

40:56.040 --> 40:58.370
He doesn't want her to have an episode
and run out to cause trouble again.

40:59.600 --> 41:01.680
By the way, ask your uncle

41:01.680 --> 41:02.850
to keep an eye on her.

41:03.450 --> 41:04.890
Don't let her get worked up again.

41:06.680 --> 41:07.520
Ms. Xiuzhen.

41:07.850 --> 41:09.890
You are the health worker
at the village clinic?

41:09.890 --> 41:10.410
Yes.

41:10.410 --> 41:11.600
I've worked here for more than 20 years.

41:11.850 --> 41:13.730
I know the illnesses and minor ailments

41:13.730 --> 41:14.450
that everyone has in this village.

41:15.250 --> 41:17.250
Do you know about Qiao Beiyu?

41:19.770 --> 41:20.600
As for Beiyu,

41:21.040 --> 41:22.770
I've definitely heard

41:22.850 --> 41:24.290
what they said about her.

41:24.450 --> 41:26.560
But I don't know for sure
if she had that disease

41:26.560 --> 41:27.730
or not.

41:29.600 --> 41:30.600
But there's something

41:31.640 --> 41:33.040
I remember very clearly.

42:07.080 --> 42:10.770
♪Perhaps♪

42:11.280 --> 42:16.980
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

42:18.120 --> 42:23.520
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

42:24.520 --> 42:30.080
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

42:35.750 --> 42:39.420
♪In the future♪

42:39.880 --> 42:45.600
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

42:47.100 --> 42:52.170
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

42:53.420 --> 42:58.580
♪That never expires♪

43:02.180 --> 43:06.650
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

43:07.650 --> 43:11.320
♪Is your name♪

43:11.820 --> 43:16.920
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

43:18.000 --> 43:21.220
♪At first sight♪

43:21.650 --> 43:24.930
♪The future has been determined♪

43:25.620 --> 43:31.180
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

43:32.280 --> 43:35.820
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

43:36.280 --> 43:40.220
♪Is a place♪

43:40.520 --> 43:46.080
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

43:46.750 --> 43:50.120
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

43:50.450 --> 43:53.920
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

43:54.450 --> 44:00.520
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
